      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is pristine inside and out, drives like a total dream, and has been kept tucked away in a garage. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and show you around this beauty!",
