    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically superlative, with a documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. Every bushing and suspension component is within OEM tolerances, delivering the precise handling characteristics this chassis is renowned for. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history, this is a turn-key example for the purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
