    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish thanks to a professional multi-stage paint correction and full ceramic coating. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue stitching remains firm and supple, with zero signs of bolster wear or aging\u2014it still retains that distinctive new-car aroma. Mechanically, this M2 is indistinguishable from new, with a complete service history performed exclusively by BMW authorized centers. Every body panel is original, the forged wheels are entirely free of curb rash, and the undercarriage is spotless. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently available. Includes all original keys, documentation, and a premium custom-fit car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and preserved in a state that rivals its original showroom delivery, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning owner. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is a definitive acquisition for those who refuse to compromise on quality or provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
