    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
